1. Allowed Uses

You may:

a. Download and use official builds of this project for personal gameplay.

b. View and read the source code for learning, review, security inspection, compatibility work, and portfolio evaluation.

c. Use this project in modpacks only by depending on or linking to the official Modrinth or CurseForge project pages, without rehosting the mod file yourself.

d. Create private local modifications for your own personal use only, as long as you do not publish, share, distribute, sell, upload, or rehost those modifications.

e. Fork the repository only for the purpose of submitting bug reports, pull requests, patches, or compatibility fixes back to the official project.

