c. Upload this project or a modified version of it to Modrinth, CurseForge, GitHub Releases, Discord, forums, file hosts, modpack launchers, or any other distribution platform.

d. Sell, sublicense, rent, monetize, or commercially distribute this project or any derivative work.

e. Copy substantial parts of the source code into another project.

f. Use the project name, mod ID, logo, icon, screenshots, branding, descriptions, or metadata to imply ownership, authorship, endorsement, partnership, or official status.

g. Remove, hide, alter, or misrepresent copyright notices, license notices, author names, credits, or links to the official project.

h. Use this project to create a competing clone, renamed copy, reupload, or substantially similar mod.

i. Use automated tools, bots, or scripts to mass-download, mirror, scrape, rehost, or redistribute this project.

3. Official Distribution

Official downloads are only authorized from locations controlled by earlystream, including official Modrinth, CurseForge, GitHub, or other pages explicitly linked by earlystream.

Any copy of this project hosted elsewhere is unauthorized unless earlystream has given written permission.

4. Modpacks

You may include this project in modpacks only if the mod is obtained through an official Modrinth or CurseForge dependency/download system.

You may not manually rehost the JAR inside a modpack archive, launcher CDN, mirror, Discord server, file host, or third-party download page without written permission.

